{"tid":978844,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"翠華驚見雞扒撈Washroom Sauce","createTime":"2019-01-12T08:35:08.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-12T08:40:57.000Z","uid":72009,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"0f03ddc6ddb50ca8c5c684c5cdb08e16ddf81671","tid":978844,"uid":72009,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-12T08:35:08.000Z","msg":"高級茶記「翠華」作為上市公司，一向都好受遊客歡迎，唔少介紹香港嘅旅遊書都有推介遊香港點都要試下翠華嘅奶油豬。做得遊客生意，中英對照嘅餐牌少不免，不過有眼利嘅網民就發現，翠華餐廳「今日推介」嘅食品「五香雞扒伴菌汁」，中文睇落唔見有咩特別，但望望個英文「Washroom Sauce」就嚇一嚇人。<br />\n<br />\n將Mushroom串錯做Washroom真係差別幾大，唔知有冇外國食家路過見到會卻步，定還是當去試吓「打大佬」？不過有錯就要認，翠華周五（11日）晚就喺facebook致歉，除咗叫各位網民手下留情「畀次機會」個同事之外，仲叫大家留言睇吓可以創作啲咩新汁，揚言會請頭50位留言網友食秘製「菌汁」雞扒喎。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20190111/large/1547210163_d633.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20190111%2Flarge%2F1547210163_d633.jpg&h=8bc44365&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20190112/59131128\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190112%2F59131128&d=b8z1wYmQJIBDRJKllPC0957TfgnX9jywtYe9GXZmhCU%3D&h=92c1fa5f\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190112%2F59131128&h=b44195ed\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20190112/59131128</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 寧pussy sauce"},{"pid":"ddecb85327c66b92562cb36c0e423c4df4600792","tid":978844,"uid":70786,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-12T08:36:36.000Z","msg":"廚房佬痾完尿唔洗手咪有菌汁囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3d5f087e8e506d90dd3af463883d3b1c52d35138","tid":978844,"uid":68081,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-12T08:40:57.000Z","msg":"講到好似有得揀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}